name: Genolution CA-X
description: This palm-sized capsule contains a single 'Core Augmentation' implant. Some speculation about the age of the containers suggests that Genolution may have kept these to be given out at a later time, however there is no doubt that the contents have been well-protected. This randomly contains one of the following four implants: Genolution Core Augmentation CA-1 Genolution Core Augmentation CA-2 Genolution Core Augmentation CA-3 Genolution Core Augmentation CA-4
